OL,6,FTributes have been paid to two women
OL,7,Fwho died in a car crash which happened
OL,8,Fnear Barry on Saturday, 2 November.
OL,10,FThe women have been named as Madeline
OL,11,FElaine Brooks, 85, and Beverley
OL,12,FPugsley, 69.
OL,14,FBoth of their families have issued
OL,15,Ftributes to their loves ones via South
OL,16,FWales Police.
