OL,4,Cand ex-BBC worker who died in car crash
OL,6,F"Beverley was a quiet lady who loved
OL,7,Fher job, having worked for the BBC for
OL,8,Fbiggest part of her life in various
OL,9,Froles and in the later as a researcher
OL,10,Ffor many television programmes. She
OL,11,Fwas still partly working after
OL,12,Fretirement."
OL,14,FSouth Wales Police is continuing to
OL,15,Fappeal for anyone with information
OL,16,Fconcerning the collision on the A4050
OL,17,Fnear Barry or anyone with dashcam
OL,18,Ffootage to come forward.
