OL,6,FSergeant Gareth Jones-Roberts, senior
OL,7,Finvestigating officer, said: "We are
OL,8,Fappealing to anybody who was driving
OL,9,Fin the area between 1.30pm and 1.50pm
OL,10,Fon Saturday afternoon and who may have
OL,11,Fany information that can assist this
OL,12,Finvestigation to get in touch with us.
OL,14,F"If you have dash-cam in your
OL,15,Fvehicles, please contact us. We are
OL,16,Fparticularly keen to hear from anyone
OL,17,Fwho can give us extra detail on the
OL,18,Fmanner of driving of a grey Audi RS 4
OL,19,Fprior to the collision."
